        "subject": "LU-957 scrub: user space tools/interfaces for LFSCK",
        "message": "LU-957 scrub: user space tools/interfaces for LFSCK\n\nControl LFSCK by lctl commands:\n\n1) scrub_start: start LFSCK with specified parameters.\n\n2) scrub_stop: stop LFSCK on the specified MDT device.\n\n3) The scrub status can be obtained through the scrub special\nlproc interface. For example: check OI scrub status by:\nlctl get_param -n osd-ldiskfs.*.oi_scrub\n\nSigned-off-by: Fan Yong <yong.fan@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I91c1f2ef50120544da23f9f729b1c68b26b34f90\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
